en.value: In a certain code language, &#39;CURD&#39; is written as &#39;342184&#39; and &#39;BREAD&#39; is written as &#39;2181024&#39;. How will &#39;BUTTER&#39; be written in that language?&nbsp;

hn.value: एक निश्चित कूट भाषा में, &#39;CURD&#39; को &#39;342184&#39; और &#39;BREAD&#39; को &#39;2181024&#39; लिखा गया है। उसी भाषा में &#39;BUTTER&#39; को किस प्रकार लिखा जाएगा?
